[REASON:planning]     *   *Supports (Legs):* Two angled struts connecting the bottom of the vertical plate to the back of the tilted tray. They need to be thick enough to support a laptop (approx 1-2kg).
[REASON:planning]     *   *Front Lip:* A small wall at the front of the tray to stop the laptop sliding down.
[REASON:planning]     *   *Side Walls (Optional but recommended):* Small side walls to prevent lateral sliding.
